<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  {% include 'head.njk' %}
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>J.D. ADAMS</h1>
    <h2>Fine Handmade Guitars</h2>
  </header>
  <main>
    <div class="hero">
      <div class="hero-image">
        {% image "src/images/painting.jpg", "image.alt", "100vw" %}
      </div>
      <p class="hero-text">Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Hic saepe sint libero ad repellendus harum doloremque. Necessitatibus animi iusto ullam facilis distinctio sequi sapiente fugit laboriosam, dolore corrupti cum maiores. Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Minima at aperiam similique dolorum dolor incidunt facilis dignissimos magnam facere. Quae mollitia quos quis vel nobis ex repudiandae iste beatae minima? Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Esse repudiandae facere quaerat deserunt, sint at odio magnam consequuntur iste maiores quasi et earum qui obcaecati nobis. Mollitia iste odit et! Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Numquam perferendis modi optio ipsa, suscipit voluptatibus blanditiis reiciendis aut consectetur illo amet? Nesciunt quam quia sed nemo facere temporibus numquam sint.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="photos">
      {% image "src/images/g1.jpg", "image.alt", "100vw" %}
      {% image "src/images/g2.jpg", "image.alt", "100vw" %}
      {% image "src/images/g3.jpg", "image.alt", "100vw" %}
      {% image "src/images/g4.jpg", "image.alt", "100vw" %}
    </div>
    <p class="cta">I'd love to build the guitar of your dreams. I look forward to speaking with you soon.</p>
    <div class="contact-form">
      <form
        id="contact"
        name="J.D. Adams website inquiry"
        action="/form-success/"
        method="POST"
        data-netlify="true"
        netlify-honeypot="bot-field"
      >
        <label for="name">Your name</label>
        <input type="text" name="name" id="name" tabindex="0" required />
        <input class="other-form-field" name="bot-field" type="text" aria-hidden="true" />

        <label for="email">Your email address</label>
        <input type="email" name="email" id="email" tabindex="0" required />

        <label for="subject">The subject of your message</label>
        <input type="text" name="subject" id="subject" tabindex="0" required />

        <label for="message">Your message</label>
        <textarea name="message" id="message" tabindex="0" required></textarea>

        <button
          name="submit"
          type="submit"
          id="contact-submit"
          tabindex="0"
          data-submit="...Sending"
        >
          Send
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </main>
  <footer>
    <p>&#169; 2023 Jeff Adams. All Rights Reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
